python3 -c ' import sys, yaml, json target = "server" with open("ansible/inventories/hosts.yml") as f: inv = yaml.safe_load(f) host_config = None if "linux" in inv["all"]["children"]: group = inv["all"]["children"]["linux"] if "hosts" in group and target in group["hosts"]: host_config = group["hosts"][target] if host_config is None: sys.exit("Host not found in linux group: " + target) print(json.dumps(host_config)) '

cd ansible/playbooks sshpass -p "${SSH_PASS}" ansible-playbook -i ../inventories/hosts.yml server.yml -K --limit server -e "hosts_to_deploy=server"
